<!-- ============================== About Us ========================= -->

<section id="aboutus" class="sec">
  <h2 class="font-weight-bold text-uppercase container text-center mt-3">About Us</h2>

  <p class="text-center paragraph container mt-5" style="font-size: x-large;">
    Somnath Education Institute is a self-governing institute established in 2017. It works as a counselling and
    guidance centre for various education institute. The main aim of SEI is to promote distance education so that every
    individual gets a chance to be educated and not fall back due to the financial issues. Distance education is one
    where a student do not have to go to the institute regularly but can complete the course by doing all classes,
    assignments and projects from his/her home. It is a great opportunity for students to study and work and not feel
    the monetary burden too much.
    SEI provides a huge variety of education courses available in the fields of Computer, Research, and Diploma with
    Certificates after completion of the courses. Usually, courses in distance education includes BCC, Executive DCA,
    DTP, ADCA, DOC, WEB DESNING, 0-LEVEL CCC, etc.
    Students can take admission from different Part of India including Delhi, Pune, Mumbai, Bangalore, Kerala and many
    other Indian cities.
    SEI offers a reasonable fee for its Students as it is aware of the fact that education is the right of every
    individual and simply because some come from low financial backgrounds that do not mean that they are deprived of
    the right to education.
  </p>

</section>
